f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好人好姐請支那人 貪平<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:10:17.000Z","msg":"冇錯，偷到secure token等同偷到private key，呢個係人為管理問題唔係系統問題。<br />\n<br />\n解決方案只有加強secure token的保管措施，唔好俾人咁易偷到。"},{"pid":"aeac25a593ca2987c5c4c5ad9231bfc8c8753fdd","tid":1797560,"uid":97389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17a37d7c3c83a631d2e37fb4078e42f23fd756bb","tid":1797560,"uid":97389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"110c12c6f75e21b87694bffa617e269cf770fc28","tid":1797560,"uid":210253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b6bffee4c0d50cad9839713973096ef1f1714d9","tid":1797560,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:01:19.000Z","msg":"破到vpn都幾勁下，要知道即使大企業係intranet 差唔多無security咁濟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:11:35.000Z","msg":"明顯係有支那內鬼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好人好姐請支那人 貪平<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:10:17.000Z","msg":"冇錯，偷到secure token等同偷到private key，呢個係人為管理問題唔係系統問題。<br />\n<br />\n解決方案只有加強secure token的保管措施，唔好俾人咁易偷到。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:15:20.000Z","msg":"來緊1月1日的加密法支共就再唔係偷，而係公然要所有人將it系統的密碼同private key上繳俾黨（國家密碼管理局）。<br />\n<br />\n舉個例即係你要將屋企條鎖鑰copy一份然後上交俾中共一樣。"}]}